A new revolution in the study of gene regulation began with the availability of genomic information and the possibility to work with abundant expression data. Phylogenetic footprinting, for instance, is a new form of leaving a great fraction of false positives out 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
after ""
