\end_inset

. Gene expression data from microarrays is the other great hope in the field to elaborate a regulatory map of human. Despite at the beginning, there was a boom of analysis of such data in different biological problems 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
after ""
before ""
key "beltran:2003a,golub:1999a,shoemaker:2001a"

\end_inset

