LatexCommand citep
after ""
before ""
key "odom:2004a"

\end_inset

. The combination of comparative genomics and expression data will become in a few years the standard way to study a group of genes as in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
after ""
before ""
key "xie:2005a"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

